overview.en: Archetypal Network is the first Ethereum based cloudmining smart contract miner to support real-time mining and high transaction throughput. Archetypal Network is the most advanced Ethereum cloudmining, supporting limit and plan orders, gas-free cancels, and the ability to fill many upgrades at once.
overview.zh: Archetypal Network是第一个基于以太坊的云端智能合约矿工，支持实时挖掘和高交易吞吐量。 Archetypal Network是最先进的以太坊云计算，支持限制和计划订单，无气体取消，以及一次性填充许多升级的能力。
